name: Format\Issue
description: The object for defining information about an issue.

properties.name: identifier
properties.description: A string that references an issue.

properties.name: order
properties.description: A number, supporting floats, that suggests the order in which the article should appear in the issue.

properties.name: tocByline
properties.description: A string that represents a byline for the entire article. This string is displayed in the table of contents.
